{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"3111a","heading":"Federal internship programs","label":"3111a Federal internship programs","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t5/ptIII/sptB/ch31/schI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft5%2Fs3111a","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextExecutive Order 13562, referred to in subsec. (c)(1), is set out as a note under .section 3301 of this title","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Regulations, , , provided that:Pub. L. 112–81, div. A, title XI, § 1109(c)125 Stat. 1615Dec. 31, 2011“The Office of Personnel Management may prescribe regulations to carry out the amendment made by subsection (a) [enacting this section].”"],"amendments":["Regulations, , , provided that:Pub. L. 112–81, div. A, title XI, § 1109(c)125 Stat. 1615Dec. 31, 2011“The Office of Personnel Management may prescribe regulations to carry out the amendment made by subsection (a) [enacting this section].”"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Internship Coordinator","label":"a .—Internship Coordinator","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft5%2Fs3111a%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The head of each agency operating an internship program shall appoint an individual within such agency to serve as an internship coordinator.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Online Information.—","label":"b Online Information.—","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft5%2Fs3111a%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":".—Agencies","label":"1 .—Agencies","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft5%2Fs3111a%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft5%2Fs3111a%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the name and contact information of the internship coordinator for each agency; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a/b/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft5%2Fs3111a%2Fb%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"information regarding application procedures and deadlines for each internship program.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":".—Office of personnel management","label":"2 .—Office of personnel management","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft5%2Fs3111a%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Office of Personnel Management shall make publicly available on the Internet links to the websites where the information described in paragraph (1) is displayed.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":".—Definitions","label":"c .—Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t5/s3111a/c","parentIdentifi